data.description: ***SELLER IS GIVING $4000***as sellers concession to buy down rate or closing costs!  or ***ASSUMABLE FHA LOAN*** 3.5%***Welcome to Sherman!  Come see this beautiful 4 bedroom home in Quail Run in Sherman.  Walk in to the open, two story entry. Off the entry is the office with french doors for privacy.  Move into the spacious living room and kitchen, perfect for enjoying time together.  The primary bedroom is downstairs with attached bathroom with shower and separate tub.  The master closest  is connected to the laundry room which is a great modern convenience.  Off the laundry room is the perfect place to hang kids backpacks on the built in wall tree.  Upstairs are the 3 secondary bedrooms and a full bathroom.  There's also a loft area that overlooks the entry.  The backyard has an extended concrete slab for the great cookouts in your future. Attic has spray foam.
